-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-181_ pf-heading-1-h3">Continuous improvement and adaptation</h3><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-183_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The dynamic nature of health and social care necessitates ongoing review and adaptation of policies and procedures to reflect emerging evidence, best practices, and changing patient needs. Regular updates and staff training ensure that hospices remain at the forefront of innovation and excellence in end-of-life care.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-185_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-186_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-187_ pf-heading-1-h3">Recommendations</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Accreditation_Excellence_ComplyPlus_Hospice_Accreditation_Standards_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1712835112" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Accreditation_Excellence_ComplyPlus_Hospice_Accreditation_Standards_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1712835112 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Accreditation_Excellence_ComplyPlus_Hospice_Accreditation_Standards_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1500x.jpg?v=1712835112 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Accreditation_Excellence_ComplyPlus_Hospice_Accreditation_Standards_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.jpg?v=1712835112 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Accreditation_Excellence_ComplyPlus_Hospice_Accreditation_Standards_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1712835112 320w" width="2000" height="1333" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, calc(100vw/3)" loading="lazy" alt="Compliance Made Easy: ComplyPlus™ Hospice Governance Guidelines - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" titl